00:06:33.399 --> 00:06:35.359
can you share more about tokens?

00:06:35.359 --> 00:06:37.600
Are there possibilities to have something set up

00:06:37.600 --> 00:06:41.320
so folks outside of our organization can request tokens?

00:06:43.359 --> 00:06:45.799
Yeah, and I think there was a similar-ish question

00:06:45.799 --> 00:06:50.079
in the chat as well about like authentication for your APIs.

00:06:50.079 --> 00:06:53.839
So in the context we presented today, taking an API,

00:06:53.839 --> 00:06:55.440
it doesn't have to be a fast API.

00:06:55.440 --> 00:06:59.000
It can be a plumber API, it can be a flask API.

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:02.000
And once you publish it to Posit Connect,

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:03.519
Connect essentially allows you

00:07:03.519 --> 00:07:05.720
to add an authentication layer to your API

00:07:05.799 --> 00:07:07.880
so that it's not just opened up to the world

00:07:07.880 --> 00:07:09.480
that anyone can use it.

00:07:09.480 --> 00:07:12.480
So in my demo today,

00:07:12.480 --> 00:07:15.760
I actually made my API essentially open to anybody.

00:07:15.760 --> 00:07:18.679
So if you open up a terminal command line,

00:07:18.679 --> 00:07:20.600
or you just call it from our Python code,

00:07:20.600 --> 00:07:23.239
you can essentially ping the same API.

00:07:23.239 --> 00:07:25.239
But I could very easily, as a publisher

00:07:25.239 --> 00:07:26.640
and owner of that piece of content,

00:07:26.640 --> 00:07:28.720
I could switch the authentication

00:07:28.720 --> 00:07:32.519
so that a user would essentially have to provide an API key

00:07:32.519 --> 00:07:35.000
to this API in order to leverage it.

00:07:35.040 --> 00:07:37.119
So in combination with Connect,

00:07:37.119 --> 00:07:42.119
you can add a layer of authentication to your APIs.

00:07:42.640 --> 00:07:45.920
Now, in terms of like these API keys

00:07:45.920 --> 00:07:48.160
and sharing with people outside of your institution,

00:07:48.160 --> 00:07:50.839
that's probably gonna be a good question

00:07:50.839 --> 00:07:53.440
for your account manager in terms of licensing

00:07:53.440 --> 00:07:56.880
and how that's gonna work for Posit Team and Posit Connect.

