00:17:09.040 --> 00:17:10.000
One thing I'll add too,

00:17:10.000 --> 00:17:13.199
that both Plumber and FastAPI

00:17:13.199 --> 00:17:16.119
provide that built-in Swagger interface,

00:17:16.119 --> 00:17:17.239
which is really great.

00:17:17.239 --> 00:17:19.119
So you can go in and you can test

00:17:19.119 --> 00:17:21.239
and play with and interact with your API.

00:17:21.239 --> 00:17:23.199
So that's baked into the framework already.

00:17:23.199 --> 00:17:24.479
So it makes it super easy.

00:17:25.359 --> 00:17:26.880
