00:17:37.680 --> 00:17:39.439
Vetiver, one of the biggest advantages,

00:17:39.439 --> 00:17:40.400
you can take your model

00:17:40.400 --> 00:17:43.920
and you can very easily serve it as an API.

00:17:43.920 --> 00:17:46.119
Because you create these cool models,

00:17:46.119 --> 00:17:47.599
but how do you actually get those models

00:17:47.599 --> 00:17:49.640
in the hands of people that need to use it?

00:17:49.640 --> 00:17:51.040
Vetiver is a great way to do that.

00:17:51.040 --> 00:17:53.640
And it'll actually create a Plumber API

00:17:53.640 --> 00:17:54.959
for you automatically.

00:17:54.959 --> 00:17:56.599
It's really pretty slick.

00:17:57.119 --> 00:17:59.839
